	(mhc-use-icon): New user option.
	(mhc-icon-path): New user option.
	(mhc-scan-month): Call `mhc-icon-setup' if `mhc-use-icon-p' returns t.
	(mhc-sch-scan1): Display icon (Use `mhc-put-icon' and `mhc-get-icon').
